Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要买那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:25.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要成为大人了 以为自己能喝就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哪里像大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:37.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算是我也有很多地方有成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那早苗就能喝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能喝啊 而且还是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,黑咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个换给你喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 我是大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:58.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:00:59.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:00.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:01.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快换给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 也有喝不了咖啡的大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过你还是个小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大人可不会干这种事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天又被高木同学捉弄了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 明天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:35.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一个人走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:38.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是高木同学不是骑车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我推着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那罐果汁 是最近新推出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:04.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:06.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这难道是什么陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要不要尝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 虽然我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:25.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样其实是间接接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 怎么样啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思了吧 你就难为情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一点也不难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个人究竟怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给你 谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:43.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喝啊 我完全不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 这点小事不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是间接接吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看 垃圾桶在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你还真能投进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一顺手就投出去了 没想到竟然能投中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原来还有这种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我也来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:02.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你往哪里扔啊 根本够不着嘛高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你要和我比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无所谓 反正我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:14.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么我们轮流投 先投进者为胜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然发起没有胜算的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来高木同学已经气昏头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这感觉真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是高木同学赢了 你要我做什么我都听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待会儿不准反悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过我不会输就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你没投中 就是我的胜利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,站在刚才的位置上 用同样的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能行 我一定能投进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:13.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就把我的初吻给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还问是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就在我投的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:41.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好的 要遵守约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要让你干什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 她想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算不让你做什么也没什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 高木同学 那不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我感觉我一辈子都没办法赢过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正你也赢不了我 这不挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思啊 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太辣舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}此处日语的「辛い」，专指食物对口腔舌头的刺激、刺痛感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是碳酸汽水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了碳酸汽水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸为什么会这么辣舌头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么总买些自己喝不了的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又在装大人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 我喜欢这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」地一下来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}日语「ツンてきた」，意为某些味道对鼻腔的强烈刺激后的表情、反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的舌头 我的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉喝了碳酸汽水之后也会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你喝喝看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,脑子绝对会「嗡」的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不会啦 不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实是来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」的一下究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的会有那种反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 想打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有反应了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在这种时候打嗝肯定会被她们嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我快要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已经忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又「嗡」地来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我走着瞧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加上回家路上被捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天被她捉弄了十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在比赛中出现失误的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:34.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作为给自己的惩罚 我会进行十倍的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我相信这样做能让我在下一次夺取胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:45.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被捉弄了十五次 乘上十倍就是一百五十次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次做的话 没什么难度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之先做三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:59.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 四…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:10.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二十…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比想象中难多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微减少一点次数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是给平日被捉弄了太多次的自己的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:28.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一边体会痛苦 一边提高警惕防止下次重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肌肉锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的手臂怎么了 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 只是普通的肌肉酸痛罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别这样 真的很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚刚的要算一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这时我应该对自己严格一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就记一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被骗了吧 肌肉酸痛挺严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这次是的的确确地被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么突然肌肉酸痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 我从昨天开始锻炼肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 要是不三天打鱼两天晒网就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼 你就尽管说吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:34.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么 今天被高木同学捉弄的次数是二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不是比昨天还多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还在坚持锻炼肌肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 姑且有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 你真的坚持下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,据说成长期时肌肉锻炼过度的话会长不高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 我也好像在哪里听说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是让高木同学长得比我还高的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那她不就会更变本加厉地捉弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过那好像只是谣言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是谣言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:27.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如说 适度的肌肉锻炼可以促进身高发育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:32.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是这样 所以你就安心继续锻炼肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得这样很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然只有一点点 但感觉你比以前变得结实了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 一言不发的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害 害羞什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你脸红了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然 你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你干嘛总是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了 因为你的反应很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 你比以前结实了是实话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,变得有点帅气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的脸比刚才更红了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的 是因为天气太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我说 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到头来 今天被她捉弄了五十四次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算上刚刚那次就是五十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:30.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 我决定就算不被高木同学捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也要坚持锻炼肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,配音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,乔尼先生 今晚要不要来咱家吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 这要看工作忙不忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是很晚才能下班 我就和次郎吃了再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:50.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然和次郎打好关系也不错 偶尔也来一下咱家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家最近很寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我要工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 再玩一会儿也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要讲关西腔啊 听到就烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了 你一点也不在乎人家的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这么说也太小气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为 乔尼先生和次郎都陷入工作无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家已经不能忍耐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然变成修罗场了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了 太过分了乔尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你是这种态度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那两只猫 都是公的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 应该叫乔尼前辈才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,呀 这不是次郎吗 一起去吃饭如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,伞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然在放学时开始下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 我可没听说今天会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没带雨衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗 你对美奈太严格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我们搭巴士回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没带钱搭巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,超级冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我借给你吧 巴士票而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 今天也被捉弄得够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不回家吗 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:44.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 我忘带伞和雨衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还真是冒失啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道今天会下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的太冒失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:03.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我记得西片的伞挺大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的相合伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会发生这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 感觉这样好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你的自行车怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明天走路上学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:35.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉刚才的气氛尴尬的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不赶紧做些什么缓和这种气氛的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被吓到了吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这种程度的恶作剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么湿哒哒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太大惊小怪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那边的肩膀淋湿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只淋湿了一点儿 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再凑近一点 好好地躲到伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:49.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心脏跳动的声音 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:56.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被高木同学发现我很紧张 她一定会来捉弄我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之 不说些什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:07.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学竟然忘记带伞 真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 高木同学出人意料地是个冒失鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我说得太过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可能也有些健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学承认自己有些健忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是什么展开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉自己好像赢了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚才我也忘了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样吗 忘了事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是什么事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像现在这样 形容两个人打着同一把伞走路的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有点想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相合伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我听不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相合伞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定没有忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个是叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:24.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情侣之间为了表达爱意 用自己的嘴唇去接触对方嘴唇那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 答不上来就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,亲 亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 雨声太大 我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨势已经比刚才小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要装作没听见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:49.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 不是有情侣用来表达心情的词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 就是那个比「喜欢」更进一步的词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开头的第一个字是「a」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}这里高木想说的词是日语的「我爱你」 即愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一个字是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我猜不出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 换成英文的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是「I」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接下来是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「I」「lo」的下一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最后一个字是「you」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:42.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 我还以为要坚持到高木同学家门口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害得我提心吊胆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我走这边回去 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘记回家的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 饶了我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
